data.description: Lovely home available for move-in immediately. Established neighborhood. Open living room and kitchen with big windows that provide lots of light. The master suite has a walk-in closet, a relaxing garden tub & separate shower. The backyard has a large stone patio and plenty of room for the kids to play. Wood laminate and tile floors throughout. Call or text to set up a showing.
